         <div class="content">
           <p>1.  To view your current location - click “Show my location.”</p>
           <p>2. You can also click on the map to drop a pin at another location. To view famous monuments and past events near your location, press “WikiGeo.” You can click on the markers that pop up to bring you to a result page that will tell you more about each landmark you choose.</p>
           <p>3. To add a marker - click “Add Marker.” This will bring you a page to confirm your location, or allows you to change your location by clicking somewhere on the map. Below, a form field is available to fill out details about your event. Press the “Save” button to add your event to our database.</p>
           <p>4. To view a marker - click “Show Markers.” This will display the markers that have been added to our database.</p>
           <p>Enjoy our app!</p>
